name: Mariamne, the True Dracophoenix
desc: If this card is in your hand: You can destroy 2 other monsters in your hand and/or face-up on your field, including a WIND monster, and if you do, Special Summon this card, and if you do that, and both destroyed monsters were WIND, you can also banish exactly 4 cards from the top of your opponent's Deck. If this card is destroyed by card effect: You can add 1 non-WIND Wyrm-Type monster from your Deck to your hand. You can only use each effect of "Mariamne, the True Dracophoenix" once per turn.
str1: Special Summon Mariamune, the True Dracophoenix
str2: Add 1 non-WIND Wyrm-Type monster to hand
str3: Banish 4 cards from the top of your opponent's Deck
